          #[span.yellow reported functional #[br.hide--desktop]impairment] during #[br.hide--desktop]the past year (Sheehan #[br.hide--desktop]Disability Scale)

    .comorbidity
      //-h1.
        Significant psychiatric comorbidity

      //-p.intro.
        Almost 50% meet criteria for #[span.yellow 3 or more] other psychiatric disorders#[sup 2]

      .nineteen.graphic
        h1.
          19#[sup.percent %]
  
        p.
          reported #[br]#[span.yellow severe impairment]

    p.footnote.
      *Data from an eating disorder–assessed subsample (n=2,980) of the National Comorbidity Survey Replication, a face-to-face household survey of English-speaking adults aged ≥18 years.#[sup 2]